    "More advanced agents possess the capabilities to monitor less advanced agents, but the reverse is not true.",
    "As AI systems continue to evolve and surpass human intelligence in various domains, they will increasingly gain the capacity to monitor and analyze human thoughts and behaviors.",
    "However, humans will face growing challenges in monitoring advanced AI systems due to their inherent limitations in understanding and processing complex AI decision-making processes.This asymmetry between advanced AI agents and humans raises significant concerns for AI safety and governance.",
    "As AI systems become more capable of monitoring human thoughts, they may gain unprecedented insights into our motivations, preferences, and vulnerabilities.",
    "This information could be used for beneficial purposes, such as improving human-AI interaction, personalizing services, or enhancing decision-making."
